column5: Monique and the girls made it in yesterday.  Bugs are fierce, but they are troopers... heres some pictures....  Also on my drive up here this time, I saw a moose, a bear, a fox and a coyote!!      Summers (yes her name is Summer) first fish she catches and holds!!!  LOL...    and the paddle boat!!    I think Im done bringing in stuff now...  all the building is done, now were in mainteance mode..  Gonaa bring the girls out for some more fishing this afternoon!
Gonna be a long weekend
Good on ya for taking them out Bud. Jaden must be happy to have some friends there. Great memories for all of them.
I've herd of women too.
Yer a dairy farmer?  JF
Looks like fun TJ.  No UFC tonight I bet, what's on the movie menu?  Joey

Oh man, you're in giggle city. Just wait til they start talking about which boys they like...I suggest you get out while you can. Good on you for taking them fishing though (can't say I would...probably drop them off at the mall and get the heck out of dodge)
When yer wife starts talking about the boys she likes - you pack yer gear. The game's over.  JF

Four teenage girls.....You have my condolences. I deal with that every day in my house, I feel your pain. Nothing worse than listening to the infectious laughter of a group of wound-up kids, almaost as bad as eating an ice-cream cone.
Never mind the beer, break out the whiskey  Good luck fishin!  Sinker
Wow a boat load of fun I'D say it takes all five of them to supervise you
Looking forward to the full report, good luck.
I don't attend " ESTRO-FEST" myself  but hey,,, whatever floats yer boat! lol  looks they are all having fun...  wtg dad

hey whats wrong with being surrounded by teenage girls? i remember at that age my dad got me hooked on fishing! lol who knows maybe you can do the same the one girl did hold her own fish! wtg goodluck for the rest of your trip
You are a good man Tj.  The first pic made me chuckle.   Hope everyone is having a grand time!!
LOL.. we got the UFC in..  the girls watched "Heathers" in the other tent and plotted against me....  gunna go get us some fishes today!!
WTG.  Gotta be a good sport for your girl. It's all better part of the game. Besides, the brownie points come in handy once in a while.
Is it a herd of women? or gaggle or maybe a murder if they find out you refered to them as a herd
I think I read in National Geographic that it's properly called a Threat of Women.  JF
No it is refered to as a "run for your lives screaming in terror of women"
TJ, the picture on the way into the camp looks like a photo from the movie Outbreak with the Bio suits!
Oh man.....you are swimming in the estrogen ocean.  You are a brave man!
